---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PostHogLayout from '../layouts/PostHogLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/footer.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<Header/>
	<main>
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="container">
				<h1>Contact Us</h1>
				<p class="hero-text">Get in touch with The Walrus Co team</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="content">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="prose">
					<p>We'd love to hear from you. Whether you have a story tip, feedback, partnership inquiry, or just want to say hello, we're here to listen.</p>

					<h2>Get In Touch</h2>
					<p>For all inquiries including editorial, partnerships, and press:<br>
					<a href="mailto:hello@thewalrusco.com">hello@thewalrusco.com</a></p>

					<p>Interested in partnerships? Please review our <a href="/partner-policy">Partner Policy</a> before reaching out.</p>

					<h2>Social Media</h2>
					<p>Follow us and join the conversation:</p>
					<p>
						<a href="https://www.instagram.com/thewalrus_co/" target="_blank">Instagram</a> •
						<a href="https://bsky.app/profile/thewalrusco.bsky.social" target="_blank">Bluesky</a> •
						<a href="https://www.facebook.com/thewalrusco" target="_blank">Facebook</a> •
						<a href="https://www.threads.net/@thewalrus_co" target="_blank">Threads</a> •
						<a href="https://twitter.com/thewalrus_co" target="_blank">X (Twitter)</a>
					</p>

					<h2>About The Walrus Co</h2>
					<p>The Walrus Co is a data-driven journalism platform committed to telling the truth through rigorous analysis and compelling storytelling.</p>

					<p><strong>Published by:</strong><br>
					Axamattic Limited<br>
					Company No. 12731987<br>
					Registered in England and Wales</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
	<Footer/>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		color: #1F2126;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 24px;
	}

	.hero {
		padding: 120px 0 60px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.hero h1 {
		font-family: 'Barrio', cursive;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 16px;
		color: #1F2126;
		font-weight: normal;
	}

	.hero-text {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: #1F2126;
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.content {
		padding: 60px 0 120px;
	}

	.prose {
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #1F2126;
	}

	.prose p {
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.prose h2 {
		font-family: 'Barrio', cursive;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: #1F2126;
		margin: 40px 0 20px 0;
		font-weight: normal;
	}

	.prose strong {
		color: #1F2126;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.prose a {
		color: #3498DB;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.prose a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.hero-text {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.container {
			padding: 0 20px;
		}
	}
</style>
